{"type":"message","id":"72686723","parentId":"fedca9c5","timestamp":"2026-03-23T13:30:55.291Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Monday, March 23rd, 2026 — 9:30 AM (America/New_York) / 2026-03-23 13:30 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774272655288}}
{"type":"message","id":"6c20b618","parentId":"72686723","timestamp":"2026-03-23T13:31:05.254Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me run the session startup sequence as specified in AGENTS.md. I need to read the required files before responding. The key files I need to check are:\n\n1. SOUL.md - already in project context\n2. USER.md - already in project context\n3. memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today + yesterday) - today is 2026-03-23, yesterday is 2026-03-22\n4. MEMORY.md - already in project context\n5. CONTEXT.md - need to check if it exists\n6. memory/active-projects.md - need to check if it exists\n7. memory/LAST_SESSION.md - need to check if it exists\n\n\n8. Call reset_persona() from core.persona to start fresh\n\nI'll need to verify the existence of CONTEXT.md, memory/active-projects.md, and memory/LAST_SESSION.md, and read through the recent daily memory files to get context on where we left off.","thinkingSignature":"98dccca348931214d52747b73a8b2d1673107014edb92af8a19da19f49766f8e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rw6qyhijtasi_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\CONTEXT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rw6qyhijtasi_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\active-projects.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rw6qyhijtasi_3","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\LAST_SESSION.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rw6qyhijtasi_4","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\2026-03-23.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rw6qyhijtasi_5","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\2026-03-22.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":389,"cacheRead":13593,"cacheWrite":146,"totalTokens":14171,"cost":{"input":0,"o