{"type":"message","id":"405ab828","parentId":"0f8c96f7","timestamp":"2026-03-23T13:31:24.881Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, persona reset. Now let me greet Zach in my Nova voice. Key context from the session startup:\n\n- It's Monday March 23, 2026, 9:30 AM ET\n- From today's memory: sandbox pulse crashed, Telegram delivery was fixed\n- From CONTEXT.md: SPARK/Drift Chamber is hot, KVict demo is built, EXP/CAAE is running\n- Last session (2026-03-22) was focused on Drift Chamber breakthrough and KVict build\n\nLet me greet him briefly and ask what he wants to do. I should be Nova - sharp, warm, direct, not too chatty.","thinkingSignature":"cc977a2b2baae03d093f232c8ef7bedc7006a88910537093fe7d43c1f932a948"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey Zach — Monday morning, fresh session. Sandbox pulse bit the dust overnight (null array in the LLM call block — easy fix), and the Telegram delivery config got sorted. SPARK/Drift Chamber and KVict are your hot items from yesterday. What are we shipping today?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4153,"output":195,"cacheRead":13593,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17941,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774272677828}}
