ng weights:  95%|#########5| 98/103 [00:00<00:00, 1964.00it/s, Materializing param=encoder.layer.5.output.LayerNorm.bias]    [0m\r\n[31;1mLoading weights:  95%|#########5| 98/103 [00:00<00:00, 1960.12it/s, Materializing param=encoder.layer.5.output.LayerNorm.bias][0m\r\n[31;1mLoading weights:  96%|#########6| 99/103 [00:00<00:00, 1972.96it/s, Materializing param=encoder.layer.5.output.LayerNorm.weight][0m\r\n[31;1mLoading weights:  96%|#########6| 99/103 [00:00<00:00, 1968.86it/s, Materializing param=encoder.layer.5.output.LayerNorm.weight][0m\r\n[31;1mLoading weights:  97%|#########7| 100/103 [00:00<00:00, 1982.58it/s, Materializing param=encoder.layer.5.output.dense.bias]     [0m\r\n[31;1mLoading weights:  97%|#########7| 100/103 [00:00<00:00, 1979.32it/s, Materializing param=encoder.layer.5.output.dense.bias][0m\r\n[31;1mLoading weights:  98%|#########8| 101/103 [00:00<00:00, 1993.28it/s, Materializing param=encoder.layer.5.output.dense.weight][0m\r\n[31;1mLoading weights:  98%|#########8| 101/103 [00:00<00:00, 1989.97it/s, Materializing param=encoder.layer.5.output.dense.weight][0m\r\n[31;1mLoading weights:  99%|#########9| 102/103 [00:00<00:00, 2003.69it/s, Materializing param=pooler.dense.bias]                  [0m\r\n[31;1mLoading weights:  99%|#########9| 102/103 [00:00<00:00, 2000.29it/s, Materializing param=pooler.dense.bias][0m\r\n[31;1mLoading weights: 100%|##########| 103/103 [00:00<00:00, 2014.18it/s, Materializing param=pooler.dense.weight][0m\r\n[31;1mLoading weights: 100%|##########| 103/103 [00:00<00:00, 2009.38it/s, Materializing param=pooler.dense.weight][0m\r\n[31;1mLoading weights: 100%|##########| 103/103 [00:00<00:00, 2000.53it/s, Materializing param=pooler.dense.weight][0m\r\n[31;1m[1mBertModel LOAD REPORT[0m from: sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2[0m\r\n[31;1mKey                     | Status     |  | [0m\r\n[31;1m------------------------+------------+--+-[0m\r\n[31;1membeddings.position_ids | UNEXPECTED |  | [0m\r\n[31;1m[0m\r\n[31;1m[3mNotes:[0m\r\n[31;1m- UNEXPECTED[3m\t:can be ignored when loading from different task/architecture; not ok if you expect identical arch.[0m[0m\r\nModel loaded.\r\n\r\n======================================================================\r\nEXPERIMENT 1: Concept Enrichment (50 concepts)\r\n======================================================================\r\n  Encoding 63 seed concepts...\r\n  Selected 50 concepts (from 63 scored)\r\n  Similarity range: 1.000 to 0.295\r\n  Steering 0.0: coherence=0.066, entropy=1.000, survivors=0, EXPLORING � moderate coherence + diffusion (on trail)\r\n  Steering 0.1: coherence=0.265, entropy=0.998, survivors=50, IMAGINATIVE � coherent + exploratory (on trail, not repetitive)\r\n  Steering 0.2: coherence=0.427, entropy=1.000, survivors=50, IMAGINATIVE � coherent + exploratory (on trail, not repetitive)\r\n  Steering 0.3: coherence=0.427, entropy=1.000, survivors=50, IMAGINATIVE � coherent + exploratory (on trail, not repetitive)\r\n  Steering 0.5: coherence=0.427, entropy=1.000, survivors=50, IMAGINATIVE � coherent + exploratory (on trail, not repetitive)\r\n  Steering 0.7: coherence=0.427, entropy=1.000, survivors=50, IMAGINATIVE � coherent + exploratory (on trail, not repetitive)\r\n  Steering 1.0: coherence=0.427, entropy=1.000, survivors=50, IMAGINATIVE � coherent + exploratory (on trail, not repetitive)\r\n\r\n======================================================================\r\nEXPERIMENT 2: Multi-Goal Steering\r\n======================================================================\r\n  Encoding 63 seed concepts...\r\n  Selected 30 concepts (from 63 scored)\r\n  Similarity range: 1.000 to 0.392\r\n  Goal embeddings: single-sim=1.000, multi-sim=0.760\r\n  single goal: coherence=0.491, entropy=1.000, IMAGINATIVE � coherent + exploratory (on trail, not repetitive)\r\n  multi goal: coherence=0.493, entropy=1.000, IMAGINATIVE � coherent + exploratory (on trail, not repetitive)\r\n\r\n======================================================================\r\nEXPERIMENT 3: Adaptive Steering\r\n======================================================================\r\n  Adaptive steering: final coherence=0.491, final entropy=1.000, steering=0.200, IMAGINATIVE � coherent + exploratory (on trail, not repetitive)\r\n\r\n======================================================================\r\nSUMMARY\r\n======================================================================\r\n\r\n1. Concept Enrichment (50 concepts):\r\n   Best coherence: 0.427 at steering=0.2\r\n   Regime: IMAGINATIVE � coherent + exploratory (on trail, not repetitive)\r\n\r\n2. Multi-Goal Steering:\r\n   single goal: coherence=0.491\r\n   multi goal: coherence=0.493\r\n\r\n3. Adaptive Steering:\r\n   Final coherence: 0.491 (entropy=1.000)\r\n\r\n4. Comparison to baseline (16 concepts):\r\n   Baseline: 0.471\r\n   Best enrichment: 0.427 (-0.044)","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774273144041}}
{"type":"message","id":"a73311aa","parentId":"ffe3e46f","timestamp":"2026-03-23T13:39:04.083Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9pztcpu34teb_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nMap concept activations to creative text using LLM.\nThe prompts here are the voice of SPARK — not Hallmark, not writing-workshop.\nReal prose. Unexpected angles. Precision over platitudes.\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport json\nimport random\nfrom typing import List, Dict, Optional, Tuple\n\ntry:\n    import openai\n    OPENAI_AVAILABLE = True\nexcept ImportError:\n    OPENAI_AVAILABLE = False\n\ntry:\n    import anthropic\n    ANTHROPIC_AVAILABLE = True\nexcept ImportError:\n    ANTHROPIC_AVAILABLE = False\n\n\n# -------------------------------------------------------------------\n# CREATIVE TENSIONS — the core of unexpected combinations\n# -------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nCREATIVE_TENSIONS = [\n    (\"light\", \"darkness\", 0.95),\n    (\"creation\", \"destruction\", 0.95),\n    (\"love\", \"hate\", 0.90),\n    (\"order\", \"chaos\", 0.90),\n    (\"birth\", \"death\", 0.90),\n    (\"hope\", \"despair\", 0.85),\n    (\"truth\", \"lie\", 0.85),\n    (\"memory\", \"forgetting\", 0.80),\n    (\"homecoming\", \"exile\", 0.80),\n    (\"embrace\", \"push_away\", 0.80),\n    (\"isolation\", \"connection\", 0.75),\n    (\"rise\", \"fall\", 0.75),\n    (\"identity\", \"other\", 0.75),\n    (\"ghost\", \"flesh\", 0.70),\n    (\"sacred\", \"profane\", 0.70),\n    (\"retribution\", \"mercy\", 0.70),\n    (\"transformation\", \"stasis\", 0.65),\n    (\"confession\", \"secret\", 0.65),\n    (\"pursuit\", \"escape\", 0.65),\n    (\"intimacy\", \"distance\", 0.60),\n    (\"warmth\", \"cold\", 0.70),\n\n[313 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774273144070}}
{"type":"message","id":"d061f727","parentId":"a73311aa","timestamp":"2026-03-23T13:39:24.943Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The push_ceiling experiment is running. Let me note the key results:\n\n1. **Concept Enrichment**: Best coherence = 0.427 (at steering=0.2), which is actually *lower* than baseline 0.471. This is surprising. The issue is likely that with 50 concepts, there's more dilution. But steering=0.1-0.3 all hit 0.427 ceiling. Interestingly, with 50 concepts the pure drift (0.0) also gives 0.066 - same as before.\n\n2. **Multi-Goal Steering**: coherence=0.491 (single) and 0.493 (multi) — slightly above baseline of 0.471! So multi-goal helps a bit.\n   \n3. **Adaptive Steering**: Final coherence=0.491.\n\nSo the ceiling is stubbornly at ~0.491. Looking at the full results, the baseline was 0.471 with 16 concepts, but expanding to 50 concepts actually made it worse — 0.427 — because the broader set dilutes the goal signal. Multi-goal steering gives a marginal bump to 0.493.\n\nThe real issue is that more concepts don't help when they're not semantically close to \"creativity\". I should focus on either filtering to only the most related concepts or increasing the connection density within the graph. Multi-goal steering barely moves the needle, and adaptive steering just converges to the same ceiling. Let me check the Ollama URL and LLM mapper status, then ship a SPARK demo with FastAPI.\n\nFor the Ollama URL, I need to hit the Paperspace Gradient notebook at `https://nyu7ryea42.clg07azjl.paperspacegradient.com` — the Ollama API typically runs at port 11434 on that machine, so the endpoint would be something like `http://<machine-ip>:11434`. I can check the notebook or run a CellsR API command to verify.\n\nNow I'll wrap up the FastAPI demo for SPARK — the drift engine and thematic graph are already built, so I just need to add the LLM mapper on top and create a minimal API server.","thinkingSignature":"4ee8cc604a1cf61a06338039dd20c5b6daa46f87664dedcdce5d9abd9000e853"},{"type":"text","text":"Good results from push_ceiling. Key findings:\n- 50 concepts: coherence **0.427** (slightly worse than baseline 0.471 — dilution effect)\n- Multi-goal steering: **0.493** (small lift)\n- Adaptive: **0.491**\n\nThe ceiling is ~0.49 with MiniLM. The path forward is fewer, *higher-quality* concepts + denser connections.\n\nNow let me check the Paperspace notebook for the Ollama URL and then build the demo.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l69t3ecx9axr_1","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://nyu7ryea42.clg07azjl.paperspacegradient.com","maxChars":2000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":36463,"output":605,"cacheRead":13593,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50661,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774273144084}}
