{"type":"message","id":"3dc55a0c","parentId":"7e924f8f","timestamp":"2026-03-23T13:50:41.719Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ollama is running locally on port 11434 with two models:\n- `stable-code:3b-code-q4_0` - for code, 3B params\n- `llama3.2:3b` - general, 3.2B params\n\nNeither is ideal for creative writing (stable-code is for code, llama3.2 is general) but `llama3.2:3b` should work for testing the SPARK pipeline. It's not great at creative writing but it will let us test the full end-to-end flow.\n\nLet me update the llm_mapper to use the local Ollama and test it.\n\n\nThe demo.py already has localhost:11434 as the default Ollama endpoint, so I should just run it directly with that configuration.","thinkingSignature":"fda89fe1bddda2950c7cd6b76beb0e0a04623b948f9e92bc28c63f853c0ab94a"},{"type":"text","text":"\nOllama is live locally with `llama3.2:3b` on port 11434. Let me test the SPARK pipeline end-to-end right now.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rkoa11xpbik4_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\Claw\\projects; python spark/demo.py --domain all --theme \"love in the age of AI\" --steering 0.3 --mode creative --n 1 --ollama-url http://localhost:11434 --model llama3.2:3b 2>&1","yieldMs":30000,"timeout":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":55703,"output":312,"cacheRead":13593,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69608,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774273833306}}
