{"type":"message","id":"2cb51ae1","parentId":"d73ea8f4","timestamp":"2026-03-23T14:04:38.077Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, I still have an issue. The `@modal.build()` method runs `ollama pull` which will try to download 4.7GB of model. This might work but it's slow. More importantly, I realize that in `@modal.build()`, subprocess.run runs during the build phase, but `ollama pull` downloads a lot of data which might timeout.\n\nActually, there's another issue: the `modal.Function.lookup` call in the image builder is weird and unnecessary. Let me clean that up.\n\nAlso, the whole approach of pulling the model in `@build()` might be slow and could timeout during `modal deploy`. \n\nA better approach might be:\n\n\n- Only install Ollama in the image (don't pull in build)\n- Pull the model in `@enter()` which has a long timeout\n- Or just let ollama pull lazily on first request\n\nActually, let me try the simpler approach: in `@enter()`, start `ollama serve` and let it auto-pull the model on first request. This is actually how Ollama works by default.\n\nLet me simplify the code significantly.","thinkingSignature":"72032768d7dd05f183f975cf38d0d776ee2857ab51614abde312a644ce5a957b"},{"type":"text","text":"Actually, let me simplify — let Ollama auto-pull the model on first request. No explicit pull needed.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_obfza5id0wik_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\Claw\\projects\\spark\\deploy\\modal_ollama.py","content":"\"\"\"\nSPARK Ollama GPU endpoint on Modal\nDeploy: modal deploy spark.deploy.modal_ollama\nEndpoint: https://spark-ollama-qwen-{user}.modal.run\n\"\"\"\n\nimport modal\n\napp = modal.App(\"spark-ollama\")\n\nollama_image = (\n    modal.Image.debian_slim(python_version=\"3.11\")\n    .pip_install(\"requests\", \"httpx\")\n    .run_commands(\n        \"curl -fsSL https://ollama.com/install.sh | sh\",\n    )\n    .env({\"OLLAMA_MODELS\": \"/root/.ollama\"})\n)\n\n\n@app.cls(\n    image=ollama_image,\n    gpu=\"A100\",\n    memory=32768,\n    container_idle_timeout=600,\n    timeout=3600,\n)\nclass OllamaEndpoint:\n    \"\"\"\n    Ollama on A100 GPU. Model auto-pulls on first generate request (~30s cold start).\n    After that, subsequent requests are fast.\n    \"\"\"\n\n    @modal.enter()\n    def start_server(self):\n        import subprocess, os, signal, sys\n\n        print(\"[spark-ollama] Starting ollama serve...\", file=sys.stderr)\n        self._process = subprocess.Popen(\n            [\"ollama\", \"serve\"],\n            stdout=subprocess.DEVNULL,\n            stderr=subprocess.STDOUT,\n            preexec_fn=os.setsid,\n        )\n        print(\"[spark-ollama] ollama serve started, pid=\", self._process.pid, file=sys.stderr)\n\n    @modal.exit()\n    def stop_server(self):\n        import os, signal, sys\n\n        print(\"[spark-ollama] Shutting down...\", file=sys.stderr)\n        try:\n            os.killpg(os.getpgid(self._process.pid), signal.SIGTERM)\n        except Exception:\n            pass\n\n    @modal.web_endpoint(label=\"spark-ollama-qwen\", method=\"POST\")\n    def generate(self, body: dict):\n        \"\"\"\n        body: { prompt: str, model?: str = \"qwen2.5:7b\", options?: { temperature?, num_predict? } }\n        \"\"\"\n        import requests\n\n        payload = {\n            \"model\": body.get(\"model\", \"qwen2.5:7b\"),\n            \"prompt\": body.get(\"prompt\", \"\"),\n            \"stream\": False,\n            \"options\": body.get(\"options\", {}),\n        }\n        resp = requests.post(\n            \"http://localhost:11434/api/generate\",\n            json=payload,\n            timeout=120,\n        )\n        resp.raise_for_status()\n        return {\"response\": resp.json().get(\"response\", \"\"), \"model\": payload[\"model\"]}\n\n    @modal.web_endpoint(label=\"spark-ollama-qwen\", method=\"GET\")\n    def health(self):\n        return {\"status\": \"ok\", \"service\": \"spark-ollama\", \"model\": \"qwen2.5:7b\"}\n\n\n@app.local_entrypoint()\ndef test():\n    print(\"spark-ollama module loaded OK\")\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":75724,"output":928,"cacheRead":13593,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90245,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774274653357}}
