{"type":"message","id":"8bd5965c","parentId":"8751cb85","timestamp":"2026-03-23T14:08:14.979Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Modal app is deployed! The endpoints are:\n- Health: `https://toxzak-svg--spark-ollama-qwen.modal.run`\n- Generate: `https://toxzak-svg--spark-ollama-qwen.modal.run`\n\nNote that it says \"Unable to detect NVIDIA/AMD GPU\" during the Ollama install - but this is in the BUILD environment, not the runtime environment. The runtime has `gpu=\"A100\"` specified.\n\nThe first request to the generate endpoint will cold-start the container and pull the Qwen model (~4.7GB, takes ~30 seconds). After that, the container stays warm for 600 seconds (10 minutes) of idle time.\n\n\nNow I'm going to test the endpoint to see if it works, then update the SPARK API config with the new Modal URL and run the full drift chamber demo with it.","thinkingSignature":"a10fb554c96d96255c2345bfcdadb88abb08a6c1ccf52fa384d384584be365a6"},{"type":"text","text":"Deployed! Let me test the endpoint and then wire it into SPARK.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8rbah7rdprbr_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Invoke-RestMethod \"https://toxzak-svg--spark-ollama-qwen.modal.run\" -Method GET -TimeoutSec 10 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":78498,"output":250,"cacheRead":13593,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92341,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774274884885}}
{"type":"message","id":"868ecf75","parentId":"8bd5965c","timestamp":"2026-03-23T14:08:22.568Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8rbah7rdprbr_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[31;1mInvoke-RestMethod: [31;1m[0m\r\n[31;1m[31;1m{[0m\r\n[31;1m[31;1m  \"detail\": \"Method Not Allowed\"[0m\r\n[31;1m[31;1m}[0m\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":7515,"aggregated":"[31;1mInvoke-RestMethod: [31;1m[0m\r\n[31;1m[31;1m{[0m\r\n[31;1m[31;1m  \"detail\": \"Method Not Allowed\"[0m\r\n[31;1m[31;1m}[0m\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774274902535}}
{"type":"message","id":"66f7c1be","parentId":"868ecf75","timestamp":"2026-03-23T14:08:42.178Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The endpoint exists (Method Not Allowed means the path exists but GET isn't allowed on that path - only POST). Let me try POST with a simple test.Actually, the health endpoint should be GET. Let me check - both endpoints are at the same URL since they're both `@modal.fastapi_endpoint(label=\"spark-ollama-qwen\")`. FastAPI routes need distinct paths. I need to fix the modal_ollama.py to have different paths for health vs generate.Wait, looking at the Modal docs - each `@modal.fastapi_endpoint` creates a separate web endpoint with its own URL based on the function name. But both have the same label. Let me check.Actually, looking at the output:```\n├── 🔨 Created web endpoint for OllamaEndpoint.health => \n│   https://toxzak-svg--spark-ollama-qwen.modal.run\n\n\n└── 🔨 Created web endpoint for OllamaEndpoint.generate => \n    https://toxzak-svg--spark-ollama-qwen.modal.run\n```\n\nBoth are at the same URL! That's the issue - FastAPI merges them. I need to change one to have a different path like `/generate`. In FastAPI, the path defaults to the function name, so I should add a `path` parameter to one of the decorators to distinguish them. Let me update the code to fix this.","thinkingSignature":"3d1d8c37ea1f8cb8a7d8cebbbfe891e85d44793a7bee7143506ec70cd4836f4a"},{"type":"text","text":"Both endpoints mapped to the same URL — need distinct paths. Quick fix.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_czr9w96dnqr2_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\Claw\\projects\\spark\\deploy\\modal_ollama.py","old_string":"    @modal.fastapi_endpoint(label=\"spark-ollama-qwen\", method=\"POST\")\n    def generate(self, body: dict):\n        \"\"\"\n        Proxy generate request to local Ollama.\n        body: { prompt: str, model?: str, options?: { temperature?, num_predict? } }\n        \"\"\"\n        import requests\n\n        payload = {\n            \"model\": body.get(\"model\", \"qwen2.5:7b\"),\n            \"prompt\": body.get(\"prompt\", \"\"),\n            \"stream\": False,\n            \"options\": body.get(\"options\", {}),\n        }\n        resp = requests.post(\n            \"http://localhost:11434/api/generate\",\n            json=payload,\n            timeout=90,\n        )\n        resp.raise_for_status()\n        return {\"response\": resp.json().get(\"response\", \"\"), \"model\": payload[\"model\"]}\n\n    @modal.fastapi_endpoint(label=\"spark-ollama-qwen\", method=\"GET\")\n    def health(self):\n        return {\"status\": \"ok\", \"service\": \"spark-ollama\", \"model\": \"qwen2.5:7b\"}","new_string":"    @modal.fastapi_endpoint(label=\"spark-ollama-qwen-generate\", method=\"POST\")\n    def generate(self, body: dict):\n        \"\"\"\n        Proxy generate request to local Ollama.\n        body: { prompt: str, model?: str, options?: { temperature?, num_predict? } }\n        \"\"\"\n        import requests\n\n        payload = {\n            \"model\": body.get(\"model\", \"qwen2.5:7b\"),\n            \"prompt\": body.get(\"prompt\", \"\"),\n            \"stream\": False,\n            \"options\": body.get(\"options\", {}),\n        }\n        resp = requests.post(\n            \"http://localhost:11434/api/generate\",\n            json=payload,\n            timeout=90,\n        )\n        resp.raise_for_status()\n        return {\"response\": resp.json().get(\"response\", \"\"), \"model\": payload[\"model\"]}\n\n    @modal.fastapi_endpoint(label=\"spark-ollama-qwen-health\", method=\"GET\")\n    def health(self):\n        return {\"status\": \"ok\", \"service\": \"spark-ollama\", \"model\": \"qwen2.5:7b\"}"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":78838,"output":825,"cacheRead":13593,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93256,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774274902575}}
{"type":"message","id":"0d1adb70","parentId":"66f7c1be","timestamp":"2026-03-23T14:08:42.270Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_czr9w96dnqr2_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"edit\",\n  \"error\": \"Could not find the exact text in C:\\\\Users\\\\Zwmar\\\\Claw\\\\projects\\\\spark\\\\deploy\\\\modal_ollama.py. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"edit","error":"Could not find the exact text in C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\Claw\\projects\\spark\\deploy\\modal_ollama.py. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines."},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774274922235}}
{"type":"message","id":"7f32eb08","parentId":"0d1adb70","timestamp":"2026-03-23T14:08:45.424Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the current file to see the exact content.","thinkingSignature":"8a97dad23634162f05c0f402000de7420690e32510889c46da3f742269709e33"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_npojydwr5fge_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\Claw\\projects\\spark\\deploy\\modal_ollama.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":79740,"output":58,"cacheRead":13593,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93391,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774274922284}}
{"type":"message","id":"204c5aba","parentId":"7f32eb08","timestamp":"2026-03-23T14:08:45.495Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_npojydwr5fge_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nSPARK Ollama GPU endpoint on Modal\nDeploy: modal deploy spark.deploy.modal_ollama\nEndpoint: https://spark-ollama-qwen-{user}.modal.run\n\"\"\"\n\nimport modal\n\napp = modal.App(\"spark-ollama\")\n\nollama_image = (\n    modal.Image.debian_slim(python_version=\"3.11\")\n    .pip_install(\"requests\", \"httpx\", \"fastapi[standard]\")\n    .run_commands(\n        \"apt-get update && apt-get install -y curl zstd && curl -fsSL https://ollama.com/install.sh | sh\",\n    )\n    .env({\"OLLAMA_MODELS\": \"/root/.ollama\"})\n)\n\n\n@app.cls(\n    image=ollama_image,\n    gpu=\"A100\",\n    memory=32768,\n    scaledown_window=600,\n    timeout=3600,\n)\nclass OllamaEndpoint:\n    \"\"\"\n    Ollama on A100 GPU. Model auto-pulls on first generate request (~30s cold start).\n    After that, subsequent requests are fast.\n    \"\"\"\n\n    @modal.enter()\n    def start_server(self):\n        import subprocess, os, signal, sys\n\n        print(\"[spark-ollama] Starting ollama serve...\", file=sys.stderr)\n        self._process = subprocess.Popen(\n            [\"ollama\", \"serve\"],\n            stdout=subprocess.DEVNULL,\n            stderr=subprocess.STDOUT,\n            preexec_fn=os.setsid,\n        )\n        print(\"[spark-ollama] ollama serve started, pid=\", self._process.pid, file=sys.stderr)\n\n    @modal.exit()\n    def stop_server(self):\n        import os, signal, sys\n\n        print(\"[spark-ollama] Shutting down...\", file=sys.stderr)\n        try:\n            os.killpg(os.getpgid(self._process.pid), signal.SIGTERM)\n        except Exception:\n            pass\n\n    @modal.fastapi_endpoint(label=\"spark-ollama-qwen\", method=\"POST\")\n    def generate(self, body: dict):\n        \"\"\"\n        body: { prompt: str, model?: str = \"qwen2.5:7b\", options?: { temperature?, num_predict? } }\n        \"\"\"\n        import requests\n\n        payload = {\n            \"model\": body.get(\"model\", \"qwen2.5:7b\"),\n            \"prompt\": body.get(\"prompt\", \"\"),\n            \"stream\": False,\n            \"options\": body.get(\"options\", {}),\n        }\n        resp = requests.post(\n            \"http://localhost:11434/api/generate\",\n            json=payload,\n            timeout=120,\n        )\n        resp.raise_for_status()\n        return {\"response\": resp.json().get(\"response\", \"\"), \"model\": payload[\"model\"]}\n\n    @modal.fastapi_endpoint(label=\"spark-ollama-qwen\", method=\"GET\")\n    def health(self):\n        return {\"status\": \"ok\", \"service\": \"spark-ollama\", \"model\": \"qwen2.5:7b\"}\n\n\n@app.local_entrypoint()\ndef test():\n    print(\"spark-ollama module loaded OK\")\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774274925467}}
{"type":"message","id":"b76ca78d","parentId":"204c5aba","timestamp":"2026-03-23T14:08:52.632Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is that both `@modal.fastapi_endpoint(label=\"spark-ollama-qwen\", method=\"POST\")` and `@modal.fastapi_endpoint(label=\"spark-ollama-qwen\", method=\"GET\")` are at the same URL. In FastAPI, when you have the same path but different methods, it allows GET+POST at the same path. But the issue is that the Modal routing might be merging them to the same endpoint.\n\nLet me add a `path` parameter to give them distinct routes. In FastAPI, you can do:\n```python\n@modal.fastapi_endpoint(label=\"...\", path=\"/generate\")\n\n\n@modal.fastapi_endpoint(label=\"...\", path=\"/health\")\n```\n\nAdding path parameters to differentiate the routes...","thinkingSignature":"f8dd1936397796b92cad827891054569b5d1f3690273f00e573aa577b930515a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nrghhctxzh40_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\Claw\\projects\\spark\\deploy\\modal_ollama.py","old_string":"    @modal.fastapi_endpoint(label=\"spark-ollama-qwen\", method=\"POST\")\n    def generate(self, body: dict):","new_string":"    @modal.fastapi_endpoint(label=\"spark-ollama-qwen-generate\", path=\"/generate\")\n    def generate(self, body: dict):"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":80464,"output":273,"cacheRead":13593,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94330,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774274925503}}
